) 11... Bxc6 12. f3 Be7 $11 {[%cal Gf6d7,Ga8c8]}) (10. Bf4 Nc6 11. Nb3 (11. Nc2
Rc8 $11) (11. Ndb5 e5 12. Be3 Rc8 13. Be2 a6 14. Na7 Nxa7 15. Bxa7 Bd6 $11) (
11. Nxc6 Bxc6 12. f3 a6 13. Kf2 Nd7 $11) 11... Rc8 ({Engines suggest} 11... a5
$5 {as a playable alternative.}) 12. Be2 e5 13. Be3 Be6 14. f3 a6 $11 15. Nc5
$6 {is well met with} Bxc5 16. Bxc5 Nd4 $15) 10... Nc6 11. Nb3 ({After} 11.
Nxc6 Bxc6 {White can try} 12. Nb5 {, when Black can go for a promising
