13. Bxa4 ({After} 13. Nxa4 Nb4 $1 14. Bxd7+ Nxd7 15. Bxb4 Bxb4+ 16. Nc3 Bxc3+
17. bxc3 Ra4 18. f3 Ke7 19. Kd2 Rha8 20. Nc1 Ne5 $44 {Black has completely
