17. Bxe7 $2 Nc2#) 17... Nd3+ 18. Kd2 Nxf2+ 19. Nd5 (19. Ke1 Nd3+ $11) 19...
Qxf6 20. Ke1 Rxd5 $1 21. Qxd5 Rd8 {Black is down a rook, but all of his pieces
