$1 23. Qc3 Qb6 24. Qb3 Qd4 25. Qc3 Qb6 $11) (5. h3 {is another unusual move.}
dxc4 $5 {Playing in the spirit of the Vienna Variation makes a lot of sense
since h3 is hardly useful for White here.} (5... O-O 6. cxd5 exd5 7. Bf4 {
