14. Bg2 Qc8 $17) 11... Qxc5 12. Nd3 Qc6 {, forcing a concession.} 13. f3 Bf5
14. Bg2 Qc7 15. O-O Nc6 $15) 10... Bf5 11. g3 Nbd7 (11... Be4 $5 12. f3 Bg6 {
is another interesting direction.}) 12. Bg2 Nxc5 {Black has won back one pawn
and retains fully sufficient positional compensation.} 13. O-O Rc8 (13... Nfd7
$5 {is another good way.} 14. Qd2 Nxd3 15. exd3 Bxa3 16. bxa3 Nc5 17. Rd1 Re8
$44) 14. Qd1 (14. b3 $6 b5 $15) 14... Re8 (14... Nce4 $5) 15. b4 $146 (15. Bf4
