$1 {[%cal Gc8f5]} 8. e3 (8. Ne5 Bf5 9. Qd2 (9. Qb3 Qb6 10. e3 Nbd7 $132) 9...
Nbd7 $11) (8. h3 Bf5 9. Qb3 Qb6 10. g4 (10. Nd2 h5 11. e3 Nbd7 $11) 10... Be4
11. Bg2 Nbd7 12. O-O Qxb3 (12... Nf8 $5) 13. axb3 h6 14. Nd2 Bxg2 15. Kxg2 Nf8
$11) 8... Bf5 9. Bd3 (9. Qb3 Qb6 $11) 9... Bxd3 10. Qxd3 Nbd7 11. h4 {This was
played in some games of Magnus Carlsen.} ({After} 11. Bh6 Ng4 {the bishop has
