Nc6 11. Rd1 Qc7 $11) (7. b4 c5 (7... Ba6 $5 8. b5 Bb7) 8. bxc5 bxc5 9. dxc5
dxc4 10. Qxd8 Rxd8 11. Bxc4 Bxc5 $11) 7... exd5 8. Bd3 (8. b4 Bf5 $5 {This is
