for the exchange.}) 12... a6 13. Nc3 (13. Na3 c3 14. Ne4 cxb2 15. Bxb2 a5 16.
Qe2 Nb4 $132 {Black has excellent control of some important central squares.})
13... c5 14. Nxc4 cxd4 15. Qxd4 Nc5 {Black has tremendous activity for the
sacrificed pawn. For example} 16. Qd1 (16. Qg4 Nxc3 17. bxc3 h5 $1 18. Qd1 Bxg2
