1. d4 d5 2. c4 e6 3. Nf3 Nf6 4. Nc3 Be7 5. Bg5 h6 6. Bh4 O-O 7. e3 {We have
reached one of the main tabias of the Queen's Gambit Declined. Black can
choose from several playable systems that promise equal chances.} Nbd7 {
This is Black's easiest way to equality. Against the main moves, Black will
